ntchurcheshostdragservices\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"$100M Leads: How to Ge...Hormozi, AlexCheck Amazon for Pricing.For such self-defined Christians, there is nothing obscene or offensive about uniting drag and Holy Communion (or whatever their particular theological tradition calls it).\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 3074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2924, \"end\": 2934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999454084915, \"rank\": 4.485482483819297e-08, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"score\": 0.999999999620286, \"rank\": 3.799190473513391e-10, \"text\": \"Holy Communion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"$100M Leads\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2850}, {\"ngram\": \"Ge\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"Hormozi\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"AlexCheck Amazon\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"Pricing\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"drag\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"their particular theological tradition\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That sacrament, its depiction in art, and for that matter any other Christian religious imagery is the possession ofallsexual identities, they'd assert, because \\\"love wins.\\\"\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3143, \"end\": 3152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999993274287, \"rank\": 6.723861023574986e-10, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"htt