 the mission of many Christian denominations, and even, sadly, many Catholics.\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3656, \"end\": 3665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999993274287, \"rank\": 6.723861023574986e-10, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3794, \"end\": 3817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_denomination\", \"score\": 0.9999995608310256, \"rank\": 4.3916924244097937e-07, \"text\": \"Christian denominations\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_denomination\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_denomination\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an effective vehicle\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3575}, {\"ngram\": \"a broader political objective\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3609}, {\"ngram\": \"the influence\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3638}, {\"ngram\": \"sexuality\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3684}, {\"ngram\": \"favor\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3693}, {\"ngram\": \"the sexual revolution\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3736}, {\"ngram\": \"whose tenets\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3750}, {\"ngram\": \"the mission\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christian rites and imagery are only a threat to this pro-LGBTQ+ movement as long as they are perceived as existing in opposition to the aims of the sexual revolution.\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 4019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3852, \"end\": 3861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999993274287, \"rank\": 6.723861023574986e-10, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"imagery\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3879}, {\"ngram\": \"only a threat\", \"from\": 3884, \"to\